WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.470
Hey, good morning family. How have you all been

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:04.990
doing? One night I was

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.749
praying. I've told you all

00:00:07.749 --> 00:00:07.759
that

00:00:07.759 --> 00:00:11.669
I have puppies sometimes.

00:00:11.679 --> 00:00:14.470
One of my mama

00:00:14.480 --> 00:00:18.870
dogs was in labor and the puppy was

00:00:18.880 --> 00:00:22.630
stuck inside of her, and she was not able

00:00:22.640 --> 00:00:25.310
to get it out. It was sideways or

00:00:25.320 --> 00:00:27.830
something. So, I tried to reach up

00:00:27.840 --> 00:00:29.589
and grab it to get a hold of it to turn

00:00:29.599 --> 00:00:31.750
it around, but I couldn't turn

00:00:31.760 --> 00:00:34.229
the dog. She was pushing as hard as

00:00:34.239 --> 00:00:36.549
she could, and I thought she was going

00:00:36.559 --> 00:00:39.670
to break this puppy in half and

00:00:39.680 --> 00:00:42.150
kill it because she was pushing so hard.

00:00:42.160 --> 00:00:43.910
Well, there was green. You know, if

00:00:43.920 --> 00:00:46.150
you've ever seen animals born,

00:00:46.160 --> 00:00:48.150
green is distress. It

00:00:48.150 --> 00:00:48.160
had been

00:00:48.160 --> 00:00:50.630
going on for hours and it was in the middle

00:00:50.640 --> 00:00:52.869
of the night

00:00:52.879 --> 00:00:54.869
during the Christmas holiday,

00:00:54.879 --> 00:00:56.950
and the vet was gone. I couldn't

00:00:56.960 --> 00:00:59.270
call him to have an emergency

00:00:59.280 --> 00:01:02.869
C-section to get the puppy out

00:01:02.879 --> 00:01:05.429
because he was on vacation

00:01:05.439 --> 00:01:09.870
seeing his kids. So, I thought,

00:01:09.880 --> 00:01:12.230
'Well, I don't know what to do because we

00:01:12.240 --> 00:01:14.149
live in a small little town.'I

00:01:14.149 --> 00:01:14.159
didn't

00:01:14.159 --> 00:01:15.510
know what to do right

00:01:15.520 --> 00:01:18.789
now other than just pray. I was

00:01:18.799 --> 00:01:21.710
all caught up with

00:01:21.720 --> 00:01:24.710
fear, thinking, 'Oh no,

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:26.789
I'm going to lose the litter. I'm going

00:01:26.789 --> 00:01:26.799
to

00:01:26.799 --> 00:01:29.590
lose my

00:01:29.590 --> 00:01:29.600
dog.'The

00:01:29.600 --> 00:01:31.190
devil tried to come and whisper in

00:01:31.190 --> 00:01:31.200
my

00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:32.310
ear, 'What are you going to do? What are

00:01:32.320 --> 00:01:34.550
you going to do?'You have all these

00:01:34.560 --> 00:01:36.149
thoughts running through your head

00:01:36.149 --> 00:01:36.159
at

00:01:36.159 --> 00:01:38.950
90 miles an hour about how I could maybe

00:01:38.960 --> 00:01:40.870
help her.

00:01:42.880 --> 00:01:44.310
You're just

00:01:44.320 --> 00:01:46.149
stressing out because you see and

00:01:46.159 --> 00:01:48.389
hear her yelping

00:01:48.389 --> 00:01:48.399
because

00:01:48.399 --> 00:01:50.550
she's in so much pain

00:01:50.560 --> 00:01:53.510
going through labor. It was awful.

00:01:53.520 --> 00:01:55.510
So, I just sat

00:01:55.510 --> 00:01:55.520
in

00:01:55.520 --> 00:01:57.670
my prayer chair.

00:01:57.680 --> 00:02:00.469
I just bowed my head and

00:02:00.469 --> 00:02:00.479
said,

00:02:00.479 --> 00:02:02.469
'I trust in

00:02:02.479 --> 00:02:04.310
the Lord with all my heart, and I lean

00:02:04.320 --> 00:02:06.630
not unto my own understanding, but in

00:02:06.640 --> 00:02:09.190
all thy ways acknowledge You, and You

00:02:09.200 --> 00:02:10.949
direct my path. You show me what to do,

00:02:10.949 --> 00:02:10.959
Lord.'I

00:02:10.959 --> 00:02:13.510
just kept saying that

00:02:13.520 --> 00:02:16.630
over and over. 'I trust in the

00:02:16.640 --> 00:02:19.110
Lord with all my heart, and I lean not

00:02:19.120 --> 00:02:21.430
unto my own understanding, but in all

00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:23.510
thy ways I acknowledge You, and You said

00:02:23.520 --> 00:02:25.990
You direct my

00:02:25.990 --> 00:02:26.000
path.'I

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:29.070
take the care out of my prayer. I

00:02:29.080 --> 00:02:31.510
know a lot of times when you're going

00:02:31.520 --> 00:02:33.430
through something hard and you're

00:02:33.440 --> 00:02:36.309
feeling the pressure of life,

00:02:36.319 --> 00:02:38.150
everything is going on around you

00:02:38.160 --> 00:02:40.150
and the

00:02:40.160 --> 00:02:42.229
circumstances look worse than

00:02:42.239 --> 00:02:44.790
ever. That's why I said, 'God, I

00:02:44.800 --> 00:02:47.110
take my prayer, and You said be

00:02:47.120 --> 00:02:49.030
careful for nothing.'I kept saying,

00:02:49.040 --> 00:02:51.509
'Be careful for nothing, but in

00:02:51.519 --> 00:02:54.710
everything make your request known

00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:55.990
unto the Lord.'I believe I just

00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:57.990
butchered that scripture, but that's it.

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:00.949
I need my

00:03:00.959 --> 00:03:03.190
Bible; my son has

00:03:03.200 --> 00:03:05.430
my phone. But

00:03:05.440 --> 00:03:06.869
I kept quoting these

00:03:06.879 --> 00:03:09.670
scriptures, and

00:03:09.670 --> 00:03:09.680
with

00:03:09.680 --> 00:03:12.070
no exaggeration, I probably quoted

00:03:12.070 --> 00:03:12.080
them

00:03:12.080 --> 00:03:14.390
several hundred times because

00:03:14.400 --> 00:03:16.790
it went on for hours into the middle

00:03:16.790 --> 00:03:16.800
of the night—3:00

00:03:16.800 --> 00:03:18.630
in the morning or

00:03:18.630 --> 00:03:18.640
whenever.

00:03:18.640 --> 00:03:21.110
It was late.

00:03:21.120 --> 00:03:23.509
I just kept quoting

00:03:23.519 --> 00:03:25.670
the scriptures and

00:03:25.680 --> 00:03:27.589
praying in the spirit, saying, 'Father, I just

00:03:27.599 --> 00:03:30.149
trust You. God, I thank You that You're

00:03:30.159 --> 00:03:33.270
moving on my behalf.'All of a sudden,

00:03:33.280 --> 00:03:35.670
it became real to me inside of

00:03:35.680 --> 00:03:38.229
my spirit. I felt a Holy Ghost

00:03:38.239 --> 00:03:41.030
gusher come out of my spirit. I

00:03:41.040 --> 00:03:43.509
started saying out of my mouth, 'I trust

00:03:43.519 --> 00:03:46.070
in the Lord with all my heart, and I

00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:48.229
lean not into my own understanding of

00:03:48.239 --> 00:03:51.270
what's going on, but in all

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:53.670
thy ways I acknowledge You, Lord, and

00:03:53.680 --> 00:03:56.309
You said You direct my path. I tell

00:03:56.319 --> 00:03:58.390
you, Satan, in the name of Jesus, let go

00:03:58.400 --> 00:04:00.630
of this! I thank You, Father, that

00:04:00.630 --> 00:04:00.640
the

00:04:00.640 --> 00:04:03.350
puppy turns around and

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:05.350
it's going to be okay,

00:04:05.350 --> 00:04:05.360
saving

00:04:05.360 --> 00:04:07.390
the rest of the

00:04:07.400 --> 00:04:10.229
litter.'Usually,

00:04:10.239 --> 00:04:12.630
whenever a puppy is stuck like that for

00:04:12.640 --> 00:04:17.150
that long, it's dead.

00:04:17.160 --> 00:04:20.550
I didn't expect this to

00:04:20.550 --> 00:04:20.560
happen—I'm

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:22.710
just telling you—I was

00:04:22.720 --> 00:04:24.710
just praying for the dog to be okay

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:26.350
and not

00:04:26.360 --> 00:04:30.629
die. An angel of the Lord walks through

00:04:30.639 --> 00:04:33.189
my front door. I'm sitting right here;

00:04:33.199 --> 00:04:35.590
my front door is over there. An angel walks

00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:38.749
through my front door, and she

00:04:41.440 --> 00:04:42.870
looked

00:04:42.880 --> 00:04:44.950
female to me.

00:04:47.600 --> 00:04:49.749
It looked like a

00:04:49.759 --> 00:04:53.510
little girl. The angel was

00:04:55.759 --> 00:04:57.670
about four

00:04:57.670 --> 00:04:57.680
or

00:04:57.680 --> 00:05:01.749
five feet

00:05:01.749 --> 00:05:01.759
tall.

00:05:01.759 --> 00:05:04.790
She walks in

00:05:04.790 --> 00:05:04.800
wearing

00:05:04.800 --> 00:05:08.469
a

00:05:08.469 --> 00:05:08.479
lattice-looking,

00:05:08.479 --> 00:05:12.710
berry-looking

00:05:12.710 --> 00:05:12.720
crown-like

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:14.629
thing on her head, like a halo.

00:05:14.639 --> 00:05:17.909
Her hair

00:05:17.909 --> 00:05:17.919
was

00:05:17.919 --> 00:05:22.310
beautiful blonde. She

00:05:22.320 --> 00:05:25.909
has a little gown on and smiles at me

00:05:25.919 --> 00:05:30.790
with the greatest grin. She

00:05:30.790 --> 00:05:30.800
was

00:05:30.800 --> 00:05:34.629
light all over; the glory of the Lord was all over her.

00:05:34.629 --> 00:05:34.639
I

00:05:34.639 --> 00:05:36.790
was seeing in the

00:05:36.800 --> 00:05:39.189
spirit, not in the natural.

00:05:39.199 --> 00:05:41.029
I didn't see physical

00:05:41.039 --> 00:05:44.629
flesh; I'm looking into the spirit and I

00:05:44.639 --> 00:05:48.390
see this angel go through my door. I

00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:49.990
just grinned back at her

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:52.629
because the peace that passes all

00:05:52.639 --> 00:05:55.189
understanding flooded my home. I

00:05:55.199 --> 00:05:57.110
could feel the presence of the Lord so

00:05:57.120 --> 00:06:06.909
strong all over me. I feel it

00:06:06.919 --> 00:06:10.790
now when I talk about it

00:06:10.790 --> 00:06:10.800
manifesting

00:06:10.800 --> 00:06:16.510
again in my

00:06:16.520 --> 00:06:18.110
home.

00:06:25.759 --> 00:06:28.950
I got lost in the moment and she

00:06:28.960 --> 00:06:32.070
just walks right in, kneels down

00:06:32.080 --> 00:06:33.550
before my little

00:06:33.560 --> 00:06:36.150
Alice, and she puts her hand on that

00:06:36.160 --> 00:06:39.350
little dog.

00:06:39.360 --> 00:06:41.110
I saw

00:06:41.120 --> 00:06:43.189
her bend down on her knees and

00:06:43.189 --> 00:06:43.199
touch

00:06:43.199 --> 00:06:45.670
that little dog with her hands,

00:06:45.680 --> 00:06:49.550
and I kid you not, I

00:06:49.560 --> 00:06:53.830
heard the loudest pop! It sounded

00:06:53.840 --> 00:06:58.950
like a cork.

00:07:07.680 --> 00:07:12.469
All six puppies came out at once,

00:07:12.479 --> 00:07:14.909
like a

00:07:14.919 --> 00:07:18.510
train. All of them were alive.

00:07:18.520 --> 00:07:22.589
Not one was

00:07:22.599 --> 00:07:26.150
dead. I helped the mama clean

00:07:26.160 --> 00:07:29.670
up the dogs and got the sacks off.

00:07:29.680 --> 00:07:32.870
I was just so taken

00:07:32.870 --> 00:07:32.880
aback

00:07:32.880 --> 00:07:34.629
at the moment and I just was

00:07:34.639 --> 00:07:37.350
rejoicing.

00:07:47.759 --> 00:07:49.990
My son was up with me praying over that

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:53.510
dog, and he witnessed

00:07:53.520 --> 00:07:55.189
everything I'm talking about.

00:07:57.759 --> 00:08:00.309
Braden, my son, he

00:08:00.319 --> 00:08:03.990
witnesses a lot of it.

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:07.270
All of them came out alive, every

00:08:07.280 --> 00:08:09.430
single one of them, like a train.

00:08:09.440 --> 00:08:11.270
We got them all

00:08:11.270 --> 00:08:11.280
cleaned

00:08:11.280 --> 00:08:14.950
up,

00:08:14.960 --> 00:08:17.110
and it was a big blessing to this

00:08:17.120 --> 00:08:20.749
family. So, I just wanted to tell you

00:08:20.759 --> 00:08:25.270
all about that miracle and

00:08:25.270 --> 00:08:25.280
the

00:08:25.280 --> 00:08:27.830
angelic

00:08:27.840 --> 00:08:30.629
encounter I had.

00:08:32.240 --> 00:08:34.149
The Lord brought it up to me again and

00:08:34.159 --> 00:08:38.269
said, 'I want you to tell my people:

00:08:40.680 --> 00:08:42.750
use

00:08:42.760 --> 00:08:45.070
scripture when you

00:08:45.080 --> 00:08:48.870
pray. Find what you're believing for in

00:08:48.880 --> 00:08:52.070
the Bible, like if it's healing,

00:08:52.080 --> 00:08:57.710
finances, or a

00:08:57.710 --> 00:08:57.720
wayward child.'I

00:08:57.720 --> 00:09:00.630
found an amazing scripture

00:09:04.720 --> 00:09:06.790
where it talks about how

00:09:06.800 --> 00:09:10.949
the devil blinds the

00:09:10.949 --> 00:09:10.959
unbelievers'eyes,

00:09:10.959 --> 00:09:13.670
and we're to pray that

00:09:13.680 --> 00:09:15.509
the Lord remove the blinders.

00:09:15.519 --> 00:09:16.829
I believe it's in

00:09:16.839 --> 00:09:19.670
Corinthians.

00:09:28.720 --> 00:09:32.470
Finding scripture to stand on concerning

00:09:32.480 --> 00:09:35.430
what you're believing for—I just found

00:09:35.440 --> 00:09:37.910
whatever I could find at that moment. It

00:09:37.920 --> 00:09:40.150
just felt right: 'Trust in the Lord

00:09:40.160 --> 00:09:41.590
with all your heart.'Lean not unto your

00:09:41.600 --> 00:09:42.949
own understanding. Because I was

00:09:42.959 --> 00:09:44.790
freaking out, I was trying to lean onto

00:09:44.800 --> 00:09:46.949
my own understanding that all my dogs were

00:09:46.949 --> 00:09:46.959
going to

00:09:46.959 --> 00:09:49.509
die and all this was going to happen.

00:09:49.519 --> 00:09:52.350
This was terrible. For

00:09:52.350 --> 00:09:52.360
the mother

00:09:52.360 --> 00:09:55.110
dog and for everything, it

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:56.990
was awful.

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:59.750
But trying to find a scripture at that

00:09:59.760 --> 00:10:01.190
moment, that's the only one that came up

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:04.630
in my spirit, and it didn't really have

00:10:04.630 --> 00:10:04.640
anything

00:10:04.640 --> 00:10:06.949
to do with speaking to the

00:10:06.959 --> 00:10:09.030
circumstances; it just

00:10:09.040 --> 00:10:11.190
rolled out of me. Just pray that. But

00:10:11.200 --> 00:10:14.710
I'm just saying, find a scripture for

00:10:14.720 --> 00:10:18.870
your situation and pray the word. Pray

00:10:18.880 --> 00:10:22.550
the word concerning what you need. Stand

00:10:22.560 --> 00:10:25.670
on that word. Believe it with all your

00:10:25.680 --> 00:10:29.670
heart and don't let it go. Let it become

00:10:29.680 --> 00:10:33.269
so real to you that it is more

00:10:33.279 --> 00:10:35.990
real to you; it is Rhema. It

00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:38.389
becomes something so alive inside of

00:10:38.399 --> 00:10:40.069
your spirit because we're not dealing

00:10:40.079 --> 00:10:41.670
with a fleshly God; we're dealing with

00:10:41.670 --> 00:10:41.680
a

00:10:41.680 --> 00:10:45.750
spirit God. He is spirit. And so we

00:10:45.760 --> 00:10:48.710
have to operate in the spirit

00:10:48.720 --> 00:10:51.670
to get what we need in the natural, in

00:10:51.680 --> 00:10:54.470
the flesh. It happens in the

00:10:54.480 --> 00:10:57.750
spirit before it happens in the natural.

00:10:57.760 --> 00:10:59.750
So what you're looking for in the

00:10:59.760 --> 00:11:02.389
natural has to be birthed in the spirit

00:11:02.399 --> 00:11:05.750
first, in prayer. So when you're

00:11:05.760 --> 00:11:07.269
praying for something and you're

00:11:07.279 --> 00:11:08.590
believing for your

00:11:08.600 --> 00:11:11.910
manifestation, find scripture because

00:11:11.920 --> 00:11:14.069
the word is what you're

00:11:14.079 --> 00:11:15.750
going to have to have. All this

00:11:15.760 --> 00:11:17.430
other stuff, the flesh—you get in the

00:11:17.440 --> 00:11:19.350
flesh. God's not moved by our need; He's

00:11:19.360 --> 00:11:20.949
moved by our faith. And I'm going to

00:11:20.959 --> 00:11:22.630
tell you, if you're begging, you're not

00:11:22.640 --> 00:11:25.110
believing. And you have to get inside

00:11:25.120 --> 00:11:28.470
the spirit first to get

00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:29.990
out of the spirit and into the

00:11:30.000 --> 00:11:31.590
natural. I'm going to say that again and

00:11:31.600 --> 00:11:33.350
again because that's how important it is

00:11:33.360 --> 00:11:35.910
for you to understand. We're not dealing

00:11:35.920 --> 00:11:38.470
with

00:11:38.480 --> 00:11:41.030
the natural; we're

00:11:41.040 --> 00:11:43.670
dealing with the spiritual. You

00:11:43.680 --> 00:11:45.790
have to understand

00:11:45.800 --> 00:11:49.110
this concerning your unsaved loved ones,

00:11:49.120 --> 00:11:51.790
concerning your healing, concerning

00:11:51.800 --> 00:11:54.949
finances, sowing seed. It

00:11:54.949 --> 00:11:54.959
is

00:11:54.959 --> 00:11:56.230
a lot different with

00:11:56.240 --> 00:11:59.110
finances. I always say I look at it this

00:11:59.110 --> 00:11:59.120
way:

00:11:59.120 --> 00:12:01.750
whenever I have a need, I sow a seed.

00:12:01.760 --> 00:12:04.949
When you have a need, you sow a seed. I

00:12:04.949 --> 00:12:04.959
sow

00:12:04.959 --> 00:12:08.069
and I say, 'Father, I put it into

00:12:08.079 --> 00:12:10.629
good soil.'And I say, 'Father, I thank

00:12:10.639 --> 00:12:12.629
you, Lord. We have a need.'Whether it's

00:12:12.639 --> 00:12:15.269
your electric, water, gas, your car

00:12:15.279 --> 00:12:17.269
payment, whatever it may be—food for

00:12:17.279 --> 00:12:19.829
your house, whatever. Father, I thank

00:12:19.839 --> 00:12:22.550
you. And it may just be ten cents. You go

00:12:22.560 --> 00:12:25.269
in there and you give that ten cents. If

00:12:25.279 --> 00:12:28.310
the widow's mite moved Jesus more than

00:12:28.320 --> 00:12:31.150
the rich man giving all that he

00:12:31.160 --> 00:12:34.110
had, how much more would He be moved for

00:12:34.120 --> 00:12:37.750
you? He's no respecter of persons. So

00:12:37.760 --> 00:12:40.310
even if you just have a penny to give,

00:12:40.320 --> 00:12:43.110
give it with faith. Give it

00:12:43.120 --> 00:12:44.870
to the Lord in faith, your church

00:12:44.880 --> 00:12:47.430
offering or whatever you do,

00:12:47.440 --> 00:12:50.069
give it by faith. Even like I said, even

00:12:50.079 --> 00:12:54.069
if it's two cents and you believe for

00:12:54.079 --> 00:12:58.470
your manifestation of some thirty, some

00:12:58.470 --> 00:12:58.480
sixty,

00:12:58.480 --> 00:13:00.790
and some hundredfold, that's just

00:13:00.800 --> 00:13:02.030
what we

00:13:02.040 --> 00:13:04.949
believe. What's a hundredfold of two cents?

00:13:04.959 --> 00:13:06.949
And that's where

00:13:06.949 --> 00:13:06.959
you've

00:13:06.959 --> 00:13:09.670
got to grow. You'll learn

