00:13:51.600 --> 00:13:54.710
you say. That's Mark

00:13:54.710 --> 00:13:54.720
11:24,

00:13:54.720 --> 00:13:56.829
somewhere around

00:13:56.839 --> 00:14:00.629
there. So, you can't doubt.

00:14:00.639 --> 00:14:02.230
That's where I have to get in

00:14:02.240 --> 00:14:03.269
there, and that's where I'm trying to

00:14:03.279 --> 00:14:05.189
tell you all a lot of it is about grace.

00:14:05.199 --> 00:14:06.389
Because I'm telling you, when the doubt

00:14:06.399 --> 00:14:08.550
